comments: After Camara (POR) sets the pick, he slightly extends his arm into Kaminga's (GSW) body as he rolls towards the basket, and the contact is marginal.
Green (GSW) does not give Camara (POR) room to land after receiving the pass as Camara steps on his foot, which affects his SQBR.
Green (GSW) reaches in and initiates contact with Camara's (POR) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Thompson (GSW) establishes himself in Henderson's (POR) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Simons (POR) grazes Curry's (GSW) arm as he starts his gather, which does not affect his control of the ball.
Kuminga (GSW) extends his left forearm and dislodges Sharpe (POR) from his rebounding position, which affects his ability to pursue the loose ball.
Green (GSW) waves his arms twice while in the visual field of Sharpe (POR) before he releases his free throw. A lane violation should have been assessed for disconcertion.
Wiggins (GSW) establishes himself in Camara's (POR) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Camara (POR) places his forearm on Kuminga's (GSW) body while airborne during his shot attempt at the basket, which is marginal.
Simons (POR) reaches in and brushes Curry's (GSW) arm at the start of the drive, which does not affect his SQBR.
Camara (POR) moves alongside Wiggins's (GSW) path and the body contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Kuminga (GSW) makes clean contact to the ball as Camara (POR) controls the rebound.
Kuminga (GSW) brushes Camara's (POR) arm as he attempts to dislodge the ball, which is marginal and does not affect his control of the ball.
Thompson (GSW) establishes himself in Thybulle's (POR) path and makes contact to his body during the pick, which is marginal and does not affect Thybulle's ability to defend.
Simons (POR) gathers the pass on his right foot and takes two steps before starting his dribble.
Thompson (GSW) briefly places his arm to Simons' (POR) body during the drive, and removes it, which Simons is able to move through.
Camara (POR) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Henderson (POR) commits a take foul on Thompson (GSW).
Henderson (POR) releases the inbounds pass within five seconds.
Thybulle (POR) establishes himself in Kuminga's (GSW) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Thompson (GSW) legally contests Simons's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Simons (POR) does not overtly or abruptly extend his leg out as incidental contact occurs with Thompson (GSW) during the jump shot attempt.
